 The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy Trivia 
 The actor for Hotblack Desiato's bodyguard in the television series, David Prowse, is best known for appearing in another sci-fi series: appearing in the Star Wars franchise as the physical performer of Darth Vader.